# KSEF Official Marking Schemes

This app implements the Kenya Science and Engineering Fair (KSEF) judging system.
There are TWO separate marking schemes depending on the school level:
- **JSS** (Junior Secondary School) — total 65 marks
- **Senior School / Non-Robotics** — total 80 marks

Both schemes are divided into THREE parts judged across TWO sessions.

